title: Modern Family AKA The Throuple | Chris Distefano Presents: Chrissy Chaos | EP 5
description:
WELCOME to Chrissy Chaos! 


This episode Chris has on his co-baby daddy on!!! Tristan Rega and they talk living the real modern family lifestyle, what it takes to enjoy life while being part of a throuple, how to raise kids the right way, what is BitCoin, was it stupid of Chris to sell all his BitCoin for no reason, the future of BitCoin, what is gold and how does it make the US dollar powerful?, Tristan thinks aliens are time travelers, how to keep a baby momma happy, theres gyms now that mine BitCoin, Chris tackles another one of the 48 laws of power!!!


Remember to rate us on iTunes and Join our Patreon for a WEEKLY bonus ep!
